lyrics:
[Verse]
Money, money, you're the culprit, the game changer
You got me caught up in this vicious cycle, all I do is chase ya
Dependent on these dollar bills, can't break free from this bondage
Trying to find my purpose, but you got me lost in the madness

[Chorus]
The problem is you, money, the root of all evil, it's true
I'm trapped in your web, don't know what to do
But I'm ready to break free, find my own way
Because my worth ain't defined by what you say
